                            <comment id="13447794" author="markus17" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2012 17:31:43 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch improving the unit test and relies on Metadata.add() in the HtmlHandler. The test adds two og:image metadata tags and checks if the og:image metadata is multi valued. The test only passes if the HtmlHandler uses an add() method.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13556287" author="chrismattmann" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 15:29:59 +0000"  >&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
